{"tid":362088,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲嘅公司咁樣無理炒人？","createTime":"2017-08-16T15:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T15:40:36.000Z","uid":137593,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb2978299b2deb9b1cb5d2a72251c5d3c43369c","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟由舊年開始係灣仔一間新開嘅日式百貨公司做pt sales。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鋪頭一路cut更，由一星期五日到一星期可以一日都冇。急要人又死都要逼你返黎，但我都懶得搵過第份就照做，做到今年六月。<br />\n<br />\n點知鋪頭話要大裝修，四層樓一齊整，逼住全部人都要休息冇得返工，等七月初裝修完再返，仲要一啲補助金都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。心諗好在我都係pt姐，諗住休息一排再返啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身公司話七月初完工，但工程成日都有遲冇早。問兩問個掃把先知原來七月底先會整好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到依家八月頭啦，個whatsapp group突然浮返出黎，dnlm原來我比佢地踢左出group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。上埋fb page先發現原來鋪頭早幾日開撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲要大事宣傳，點知就炒撚晒啲員工。我啲私人野仲放係locker啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返員工守則都話係員工犯左大錯都有3次warning先炒得，就算係即日炒個啲都有七日嘅薪日做賠償，當提前左七日通知啦。有冇巴絲知道如果佢咁樣炒晒我地啲員工岩唔岩架？有冇得告佢啲咩架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢間公司連炒人都唔正式同人講聲/賠償，令人條氣真係好唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。自問做野都好認真，冇犯咩大錯，整花晒我嘅cv，仲要白白等佢裝修幾個月，浪費晒啲時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想知做乜會比人炒咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：公司正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，樓豬梗係去追究啦。係我條氣都唔順啦，仲可以賺多七日糧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：公司冇做錯，想炒你咪炒你，肯賠你都偷笑啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93d0dae6f33aa2600757de563da90fe1f31fb98","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:10:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7e7c44074c6686318fbdf3ea691dce1c671b7503","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:10:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"82386249f128eda439446e20a776baa17612ec81","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:10:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"de90bc8e598f7677adecc9d532128c60e85ceee1","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:11:05.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d86decbe598b72c721eb9c51eeee9e586a456f77","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:11:15.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"86234524e4a53e2660886100aa2c2c1b1e4044e8","tid":362088,"uid":46281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:15:42.000Z","msg":"咁樓主啲嘢有無聯絡過啲人點拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8447c160d4cea6686bdcf56d3ab934b81ca7efde","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樓主啲嘢有無聯絡過啲人點拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。印象中入面除左制服，仲有本書同一堆膠叉同潤唇膏。"},{"pid":"a623c89895528a04ff4db88c28097411e69947a3","tid":362088,"uid":137593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT